

############# Customer Api ###############

-> Register User

Post Mapping ->http://localhost:8080/NihilentBank/register

{
     "customerId":"U001",
    "name":"Aniket",
     "emailId":"aniket@gmail.com",
     "password":"Aniket@123",
     "mobileNumber":982365149,
     "roles":"Admin",
     "address":"Bhandara",
     "gender":"Male"
}
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-> Authenticate 

post Mapping -> http://localhost:8080/NihilentBank/auth

{
    "username":"aniket@gmail.com",
    "password":"Aniket@123"
}

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
role-> Admin
Get Mapping -> http://localhost:8080/NihilentBank/admin

Send Jwt token 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
role-> user
Get Mapping -> http://localhost:8080/NihilentBank/user

Send Jwt token 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Get mapping-> http://localhost:8080/NihilentBank/admin/getCustomers

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

#Bank Account

create Account 
Post Mapping:-> http://localhost:8080/NihilentBank/admin/createAccount

{

    "accountNumber":123456672,
    "bankName":"HDFC Bank",
    "ifscCode":"HDFC000123",
    "accountType":"SAVING",
    "balance":1000,
    "panCard":"ABCD998D",
    "accountStatus":"ACTIVE",

   "customerDto":
    {
        "mobileNumber":8176373832
    }

}
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 Get Account Details
Get Mapping-> http://localhost:8080/NihilentBank/admin/accountDetails/12345667

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


Get Balance 

Get Mapping -> http://localhost:8080/NihilentBank/user/getBalance/123456672

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------


#Digital BankAccount

Link Account

Get Mapping-> http://localhost:8080/NihilentBank/user/linkAccount?mobileNumber=8176373831&accountNumber=12345667


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


#Transaction 


fund Transfer

post Mapping -> http://localhost:8080/NihilentBank/user/fundTransfer

{
